PHASE 2
The Network Begins
Adventure 2 | 15–40% | Party: 3 AP
8–12 nodes across three holds. She can feel them — not much, not power yet, but awareness. She knows where every node is, whether it's active, approximately when each person will reach their final position. The network is a nervous system and she has just become aware she has one.
The body has fully reintegrated. She moves with more economy. Less adjustment. She has processed most of what she needed to process about the current world.
Reconstruction: 2–3 hours. New Passive — Network Sense: Knows location, status, and position of every active node at all times. Knows immediately if a node is disturbed or destroyed. Cannot be deceived about the ritual's current state. New Passive — Node Proximity: Within one mile of an active node, all FP costs reduced by 1.

