PHASE 4
The Land Responds
Adventure 4 | 65–90% | Party: 5 AP
35–40 nodes across seven holds. She can feel the geographic shape of the whole pattern. The cold flows between nodes. The land has been quietly reorganizing itself around her arithmetic. She is drawing real power from this.
She tells them what the ritual does to the nodes. In Riften. Directly. Without preamble, without apology, without uncertainty.
